Paper: hep-th/9502087

Date: 1995-02-14

Title: BRST - BFV analysis of anomalies in bosonic string theory interacting

with background gravitational fieldAuthors: I.L. Buchbinder, B.R. Mistchuk, V.D. Pershin

Comments: 11 pages, LATEX, no figures

Journal-ref: Phys. Lett. B353 (1995) 457

The general BRST-BFV analysis of anomaly in the string theory coupled tobackground fields is carried out. An exact equation for c-valued symbol ofanomaly operator is found and structure of its solutions is studied.